{"tid":1161580,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中美傳擱置談判震散美股","createTime":"2019-05-19T09:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T11:54:51.000Z","uid":48286,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a42f7b4980f2abd61ae56e75e81ea893fbb3efbf","tid":1161580,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"中美貿易戰重燃震散美股。美國特朗普政府發難封殺華為下，中美貿易戰談判傳出擱置。消息蓋過業績和數據提振利好，美股上周五全面低收，三大指數一周計亦全部見紅。美國多家百貨公司和零售集團本周公佈業績，縱首季表現料未受中美貿易戰關稅大影響，最新展望卻令投資者密切注視。聯儲局本周公佈5月會議紀錄，主席鮑威爾（Jerome Powell）則會在另一場合演說，市場關注聯儲局會否部署減息托市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFrom:HKET"},{"pid":"5e795a68807c5d8c067a20c69706d9ffbe209a1a","tid":1161580,"uid":247972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"減息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25e9e1d7b77cb6166864c79fbe6498af23e2b0d1","tid":1161580,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:15:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b00750cddc1d79ef195b2c2fb3628d7d3fb9e068","tid":1161580,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"加緊25% 都仲拖? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32dfaf7ca3ccdac4b4ccdab32ed60ef7fe585229","tid":1161580,"uid":19725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"美國佬無乜用 真係中晒中國毒"}]}